# CMOS Inverter Design

Tool Used: Cadence Virtuoso

## Aim
To design and simulate a CMOS NOT inverter.

## Components Used
PMOS transistor
NMOS transistor
Power supply (VDD)
Ground (GND)

## Working Principle

When Input = 0  
PMOS turns ON  
NMOS turns OFF  
Output = 1

When Input = 1  
PMOS turns OFF  
NMOS turns ON  
Output = 0

## Conclusion
The CMOS inverter produces the complement of the input signal and is the basic building block of digital circuits.
